# Payment setup — Quickpay + Verifone POS Cloud

**Always reference the official documentation below** before implementing or changing anything related to payments, checkout, webhooks, merchant onboarding, or terminal integration. Do not guess API shapes, flows, or compliance behavior — verify against the docs.

## Two payment rails (by channel)

| Channel | Provider | Where in the app |
|---------|----------|------------------|
| **Online** (self-service shop, CNP) | **Quickpay** | `Client/src/app/features/checkout/` + server Quickpay adapter |
| **In-store** (kasse + physical terminal, card-present) | **Verifone POS Cloud** | `Client/src/app/features/kasse/` + server Verifone adapter |

Do **not** use Verifone eCommerce / Hosted Checkout for web — online goes through **Quickpay**.

